headline: CoStar Group to Present at KBW Fintech Conference
summary: WASHINGTON, November 12, 2024--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, and analytics in the property markets, will present at this year’s KBW Fintech Conference. CFO Chris Lown and Head of Investor Relations Rich Simonelli will participate in a fireside chat on Thursday, November 14, 2024, at 12:40 p.m. ET. Live and recorded versions of the webcast will both be available under the Events & Presentations section of the CoStar Group In

headline: Baird Q3 2024 Mid Cap Growth Equity Fund Commentary
summary: For the quarter, the Baird Mid Cap Growth portfolio produced a positive return of +5.2%, net of fees, trailing the Russell Midcap Growth increase of +6.5%.
